Mapinformations:
****************

This map is about a german musicals names "Tanz der Vampire" [GER] (Eng.: "Dance
of the vampire"). But in this luxus-jail isn't only the musical! 

You can find there a swimplace. Its look like in a junge and there is very big tree 
where you can go up and jump in the water. You can see behind the big tree a 
very big waterslide!

In one room you see a aquarium, where you can go in from the room over it.

There is a footballroom. You can change between 3 floors and 8 balls.
Goals come up, when you press a button.

You can visit a big room with a lot of crates. You can destroy them. It's funny!

The weapon-room was blow upped from any person and the securityguy is killed. You
can go to the weapon-room throug a destroyed elevator.

The CT's start in the weapon-room and can either go directly to the cells or throug
the destroyed elevator in an other room.

The T's start in there cells. There aren't any weapons in.

Hafe Fun & Good Look in my Map and enjoy my fantasie!
